**Here's a full, clean breakdown of exactly how the ASCII Pet system should work:**

### Core Concept: The Ọ̀ṣỌ́ Pet System

Every pet has **one consistent sacred element** — the **Ọ̀ṣỌ́ mask** — which only appears on the highest tier. Everything else changes to create massive variety.

### 1. Tier & Rarity Structure

| Tier | Rarity      | Name              | Face Style                  | How Common |
|------|-------------|-------------------|-----------------------------|------------|
| 0    | Newborn     | Baby / Blank      | Very simple dots or lines   | Extremely common |
| 1    | Common      | Basic Pet         | Simple eyes (• •) (o o)     | Very common |
| 2    | Uncommon    | Evolved Pet       | Stylized eyes (◕ ◕) (◉ ◉)  | Common |
| 3    | Rare        | Powerful Pet      | Sharp/detailed eyes (◆ ◆)   | Rare |
| 4    | Epic        | Legendary Pet     | Ornate & glowing eyes       | Very rare |
| 5    | Sovereign   | Ọ̀ṣỌ́ Mask         | **Full Ọ̀ṣỌ́ as the actual face** | Extremely rare |

### 2. Face Rules (Most Important)

- **Tiers 0–4**: Use normal eyes + mouth. No Ọ̀ṣỌ́.
- **Tier 5 only**: The actual **Ọ̀ṣỌ́** becomes the literal face (left eye, nose, right eye).
- This makes seeing an Ọ̀ṣỌ́ mask on a pet feel very special — like seeing a shiny Pokémon.

### 3. What Makes Each Pet Unique

Even within the same tier, pets differ in 5 areas:

- **Body Shape** (quadruped, floating orb, serpent, mechanical, etc.)
- **Aura / Particles** (sparkles, flames, mist, runes, lightning, etc.)
- **Color Scheme** (done via ANSI colors in terminal, CSS in browser)
- **Personality Expression** (curious, bold, calm, mischievous, stoic)
- **Special Details** (horns, wings, tails, runes, jewelry)

### 4. Animation System

Every pet gets 4–6 animation frames:
- Idle breathing
- Blinking
- "Thinking" animation (when user sends a `think` command)
- Happy / Excited (when reputation increases)
- Evolution animation (big moment when hitting Tier 5)

The **Ọ̀ṣỌ́ mask stays completely still** in every frame — only the body, aura, and particles move.

### 5. Evolution Flow (How pets grow)

- Starts as Tier 0 (very plain)
- Slowly gains detail as reputation increases
- At Tier 5, it transforms into the sacred **Ọ̀ṣỌ́ mask** — the ultimate form
- Once it reaches Tier 5, it keeps the mask permanently

### 6. Dashboard Layout (Final Vision)

The screen should look like this:

```
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                    Your Pet — "Luna"                         ║
║                                                              ║
║ ║
║                   (Animated + Breathing)                     ║
║                                                              ║
║  Reputation: 87/100     Tier 4 — Epic                        ║
║                                                              ║
║  Unlocked Tools:                                             ║
║   • Web Search      • Image Generation      • Code Helper   ║
║                                                              ║
║  Chat: __________________________________________________    ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

